President Barack Obama is scheduled to deliver the commencement address at the US Naval Academy in Annapolis, Maryland on May 22, 2009. The Naval Academy is handling all media logistics and credentialing for the event. The deadline to request credentials is today, May 20th, at 4:00 PM EDT. For more information and to request credentials, visit http://www.usna.edu/PAO/vpk09/indexvpk09.htm or contact Jennifer Erickson at (410) 293-2292 or erickson@USNA.edu.